       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI77702.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI77702.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Lista Ausęncias                                            *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI77702         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3002 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV7770.
       COPY COCV7771.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY ARCL0039.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-2                       VALUE '2'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-3                       VALUE '3'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-4                       VALUE '3'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3002 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3002'                  .
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-AP       PIC X(02) VALUE 'AP'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-ANO                 PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 FILLER                 PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-MES                 PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 FILLER                 PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DIA                 PIC  X(02)  VALUE '01'.

           05 WS-FIM                    PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CPERIOD                 PIC X(07) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-CPERIOD.
             10 WS-CPERIOD-AA              PIC X(04) VALUE SPACES.
             10 WS-CPERIOD-SLH             PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.
             10 WS-CPERIOD-MM              PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI77702'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 WS-CPERIOD-MIN             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CPERIOD-MAX             PIC  X(03) VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN        PIC  X(08) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX        PIC  X(08) VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-DDATAUS-MIN            PIC  X(07) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATAUS-MIN.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-ANO     PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-SEP     PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MIN-MES     PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 WS-DDATAUS-MAX            PIC  X(07) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DDATAUS-MAX.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-ANO     PIC  X(04)  VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-SEP     PIC  X(01)  VALUE '-'.
              10 WS-DDATAUS-MAX-MES     PIC  X(02)  VALUE SPACES.

           05 FILLER                    PIC  X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT30 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                        CPERIOD
                      , NIDPROJECTO
                      , DPAG
                      , CUSERID
                      , HTIMEST
                      , ISTATUS
                      , MFACTURA
                   FROM COVT3002_PARMVENC
                  WHERE   CPERIOD     = :COCD3002-CPERIOD
               ORDER BY CPERIOD
                      , NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI77702         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------

       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV7770-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7770-ASE               TO COCV7771-ASE.

      *    INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS
      *               COCV7771-ADE          REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
      *                                          ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7770-ADE                TO COCV7771-ADE.

           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2103-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV7771-CPERIOD-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-SEM-DADOS
                      TO COCV7771-CPERIOD-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV7771-CPERIOD-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF

              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


       2103-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *    MOVE COCV7770-CPERIOD           TO COCD3002-CPERIOD.

           MOVE COCV7770-CANO              TO WS-CPERIOD-AA.
           MOVE '-'                        TO WS-CPERIOD-SLH
           MOVE COCV7770-CMES              TO WS-CPERIOD-MM.
           MOVE WS-CPERIOD                 TO COCD3002-CPERIOD.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT30
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3002               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT30
              INTO
                  :COCD3002-CPERIOD
                , :COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO
                , :COCD3002-DPAG
                , :COCD3002-CUSERID
                , :COCD3002-HTIMEST
                , :COCD3002-ISTATUS
                , :COCD3002-MFACTURA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT3002               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                OR WS-FIM = 'F'
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG1
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS1
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG1
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO2 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO2
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG2
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS2
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG2
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO3 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO3
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG3
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS3
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG3
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO4 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO4
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG4
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS4
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG4
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO5 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO5
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG5
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS5
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG5
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO6 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO6
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG6
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS6
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG6
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO7 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO7
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG7
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS7
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG7
           ELSE
           IF COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO8 EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE COCD3002-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO8
               MOVE COCD3002-DPAG         TO COCV7771-DPAG8
               MOVE COCD3002-ISTATUS      TO COCV7771-ISTATUS8
               MOVE COCD3002-MFACTURA     TO COCV7771-VALPAG8
               MOVE 'F'                   TO WS-FIM
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT30
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
               MOVE 'COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
               MOVE  COCV7771-NIDPROJECTO1  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
               MOVE 'COCV7771-DPAG1      '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
               MOVE  COCV7771-DPAG1         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
               MOVE 'COCV7771-DPAG2      '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
               MOVE  COCV7771-DPAG2         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
               MOVE 'COCV7771-DPAG3      '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
               MOVE  COCV7771-DPAG3         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE COCV7771-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV7771-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7771-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCR0039 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
